  "course_description": "This course introduces students to the basics of Kuchipudi, an Asian Indian classical dance form of South India based on dance dramas that tell a story. Students will gain familiarity with hand gestures, foot movements, rhythmic syllables, and how to use combinations of these to express themselves through dance. This course culminates in a performance or lecture demonstration.",
